{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeMinWidthSmall"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMinWidthSmall"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._550"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeMinWidthSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC17sizeMinWidthSmallSdvp","title":"sizeMinWidthSmall","role":"symbol"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeminwidthsmall"]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"LinkComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"links","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider/sizeMinWidthSmall":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeMinWidthSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizeMinWidthSmall","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeminwidthsmall","type":"topic","title":"sizeMinWidthSmall","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token DimensionRawTokens._550","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"ic_theme_orange